%N A397040 Convolution of A000005 and A026007.
%H A397040 Vaclav Kotesovec, <a href="/A397040/b397040.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000</a>
%F A397040 G.f.: Sum_{j>=1} (x^j/(1-x^j)) * Product_{k>=1} (1+x^k)^k.
%F A397040 a(n) ~ A026007(n) * 3*n^(1/3) * (log(3*n^(1/3)/(2*r)) + gamma) / (2*r), where r = (3/2)^(4/3) * zeta(3)^(1/3) and gamma is the Euler-Mascheroni constant A001620.
%F A397040 a(n) ~ exp(3^(4/3) * zeta(3)^(1/3) * n^(2/3) / 2^(4/3)) * (log((2*n/(3*zeta(3)))^(1/3)) + gamma) / (2^(5/12) * 3^(2/3) * sqrt(Pi) * zeta(3)^(1/6) * n^(1/3)).
%t A397040 nmax = 40; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[x^j/(1-x^j),{j,1,nmax}] * Product[(1+x^k)^k, {k,1,nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x]
